{"tid":814114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無懼特朗普!  日本首相反對貿易制裁","createTime":"2018-09-11T03:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T14:55:24.000Z","uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"45e07eaf4e6a7163b22ed607402afbf94b49d489","tid":814114,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T03:52:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%84%A1%E6%87%BC%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE-%E5%AE%89%E5%80%8D%E6%99%89%E4%B8%89%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE%E6%8D%8D%E8%A1%9B%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93-024245861.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2587%25BC%25E5%25B7%259D%25E6%2599%25AE-%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2580%258D%25E6%2599%2589%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AB%25BE%25E6%258D%258D%25E8%25A1%259B%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593-024245861.html&d=G6Do748NN7a8wppDrpWp1%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4368d9c6\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%84%A1%E6%87%BC%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE-%E5%AE%89%E5%80%8D%E6%99%89%E4%B8%89%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE%E6%8D%8D%E8%A1%9B%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93-024245861.html</a></span><br />\n<br />\n無懼川普 安倍晉三承諾捍衛自由貿易<br />\nBloomberg 彭博\t<br />\n<br />\n&bull;\t2018年9月11日 上午10:42<br />\n<br />\n美國總統 川普再度施壓，要求日本簽署雙邊貿易協議，而首相 安倍晉三在政策演講中，承諾捍衛自由貿易。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「以牙還牙的貿易制裁對任何國家都沒有好處，」安倍周一在自民黨籍議員的會議上說。</strong>「現在是時候由日本擔任自由貿易的旗手，率先制定新時代的規則。」他沒有提及川普的名字。<br />\n<br />\n上周五，川普向記者表示，如果日本沒有與美國達成新的貿易協議，日本將面臨「 大問題」。上周稍早，川普接受《華爾街日報》訪問時說，他與日本領導層的關係不錯，但是一旦他說出日本需要 付多少錢，良好關係就會結束。<br />\n<br />\n雖然安倍沒有直接回應川普最新帶刺的話，但美國的貿易制裁對他上任近6年來所聲稱的經濟成長 主要政績，正構成步步緊逼的威脅。安倍這次演講是與他的競爭對手前防衛大臣 石破茂首度交鋒，他們倆人都正式宣布參選自民黨黨魁。執政的自民黨將於9月20日舉行黨魁選舉。"},{"pid":"f88619f8ec50d23461f605c502c177480b0aeec6","tid":814114,"uid":198583,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T03:55:04.000Z","msg":"崇日撚進場未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"941e6cec58c645d5f621f9db389f5e8fc8df7507","tid":814114,"uid":61484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T04:02:04.000Z","msg":"係咪冇曬原材料要同強國用技術交換<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"affb6b86b3087925a7d47bf95b8be2893ccb50ed","tid":814114,"uid":57376,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T04:07:46.000Z","msg":"安倍這次演講是與他的競爭對手前防衛大臣 石破茂首度交鋒，他們倆人都正式宣布參選自民黨黨魁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為左爭選咋<br />\n選完會繼續奶美國鞋底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc03795319e7108e58e996a8f8cff5c3cf6b809","tid":814114,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T04:09:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d866410700e892bae4c644cd3144563c7ca90457","tid":814114,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T04:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee2025bf7a767b722a36fb1c0fc8a7695c553da9","tid":814114,"uid":76216,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T04:57:23.000Z","msg":"日本狗養唔熟嫁啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以早幾十年日本一發起就比美國打爆佢泡沫"},{"pid":"6ae6b4bdae754f905e78f10cfc6352b801b61e23","tid":814114,"uid":208074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T05:00:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98fcc79d4f6a09f425a221f750e47d97f8d4b67e","tid":814114,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"affb6b86b3087925a7d47bf95b8be2893ccb50ed","tid":814114,"uid":57376,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T04:07:46.000Z","msg":"安倍這次演講是與他的競爭對手前防衛大臣 石破茂首度交鋒，他們倆人都正式宣布參選自民黨黨魁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為左爭選咋<br />\n選完會繼續奶美國鞋底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T05:06:12.00